{"tid":2213381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4小粉紅憤怒記","createTime":"2020-09-22T13:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T13:50:55.000Z","uid":58164,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7aecbefc19ffd421e8687d498e6c6c3b9acc9617","tid":2213381,"uid":58164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的 昨晚打gvg街場<br />\n拍左件大陸狗 之後打輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3UAa0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3UAa0X.jpg&h=4399ad38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後佢竟然屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxVjCHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxVjCHf.jpg&h=f53c557c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最撚嘔心係今朝訓醒發現PlayStation send左封通知黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PT0LygV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPT0LygV.jpg&h=d2ea27f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NafVvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NafVvi.jpg&h=e4d419eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話我違反左社群條款<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我自己就唔順條氣打電話上去問<br />\n官方就話訊息已經被系統刪左<br />\n所以條小粉紅咩事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係佢嘈先仲要侮辱埋我<br />\n但係得我被警告 而家條氣真係好唔撚順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係咪連PlayStation官方都小粉紅至上主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5420e714dc62aca2d75bb026961c0f6b708b013","tid":2213381,"uid":58164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df169cb6f53965b274edfb74594b22cc2ff7dcf","tid":2213381,"uid":520